body:
@Morello, Xelnath, and other rioters.

I noticed while on Howling Abyss earlier, you cannot acquire poro-snax with the buscuiteer replacement mastery (Culinary Master). Now I haven't tried every other mastery, but I presumed that one would still grant them. The fact that I can no longer help my little poros grow makes me sad.

{{item:2052}} Please Rito, think of the poor starving poros! {{item:2052}} 

Without us to feed them, they will go extinct and the watchers will easily reclaim the world.
